                <mxCell id="P0C3" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(21, 128, 61);&quot;&gt;🔍 Audit &amp;amp; Gate&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bundle Analyzer (source-map-explorer)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lighthouse CI (audit headless)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Performance Budget Gate (block deploy)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;ESLint perf rules · tsc --noEmit&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Test coverage gate&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#15803d;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#14532d;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
