                <mxCell id="P0C2" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(21, 128, 61);&quot;&gt;📦 Bundle &amp;amp; Optimize&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tree-Shaking (loại dead code)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;esbuild Builder (build nhanh 10×)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Code splitting (lazy chunks)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asset Versioning (outputHashing=all)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Bundle Budget (cảnh báo size)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#15803d;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#14532d;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
