                <mxCell id="P1C4" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(3, 105, 161);&quot;&gt;💾 Server-side Cache&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Browser HTTP cache (Cache-Control, ETag)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CDN edge cache (stale-while-revalidate)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Redis / API cache (BFF layer)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reverse proxy cache (Nginx · Varnish)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;HTTP 304 Not Modified (validation)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#0369a1;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#0c4a6e;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
