                <mxCell id="P1C3" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(3, 105, 161);&quot;&gt;🪓 Code Splitting &amp;amp; Lazy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lazy Loading Routes (loadComponent)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Preloading Strategy (Quicklink)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Standalone Components&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Module Federation (micro-frontends)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Asset Versioning (outputHashing)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#0369a1;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#0c4a6e;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
