                <mxCell id="P2C1" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(180, 83, 9);&quot;&gt;🖌️ Critical CSS &amp;amp; Scripts&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Inline critical CSS above-the-fold&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Consolas, monospace;&quot;&gt;&amp;lt;script async&amp;gt;&lt;/span&gt; / &lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Consolas, monospace;&quot;&gt;defer&lt;/span&gt; (không block parse)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;CSS containment (&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Consolas, monospace;&quot;&gt;contain: layout&lt;/span&gt;)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tránh @import CSS lồng nhau&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Loại CSS không dùng (PurgeCSS)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#b45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#78350f;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-1480" y="158" width="280" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="P2C2" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(180, 83, 9);&quot;&gt;🖼️ Image &amp;amp; Media (LCP)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;NgOptimizedImage (priority, srcset)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;AVIF / WebP format · responsive images&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Lazy load images dưới fold (loading=lazy)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Image CDN (on-the-fly resize)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Fetch priority hint (fetchpriority=high)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#b45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#78350f;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-1480" y="348" width="280" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="P2C3" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(180, 83, 9);&quot;&gt;🔤 Font Strategy&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;font-display: swap (tránh invisible text)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Preload font file critical&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Subset font (chỉ ký tự cần dùng)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Self-host font (tránh CORS round trip)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Variable font (1 file thay nhiều weight)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#b45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#78350f;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-1480" y="538" width="280" height="170" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="P2C4" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(180, 83, 9);&quot;&gt;💧 Hydration &amp;amp; @defer&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Hydration (resume từ SSR DOM)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Incremental Hydration (Angular 19+)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;@defer Block (viewport / idle / on interaction)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;provideClientHydration()&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;View Transitions API&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#b45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#78350f;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
