                <mxCell id="P2C5" value="&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 13px; color: rgb(180, 83, 9);&quot;&gt;📐 Layout Stability (CLS)&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Set width/height cho image, video, iframe&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Reserve space cho ad / embed&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tránh inserting content above existing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: Consolas, monospace;&quot;&gt;contain-intrinsic-size&lt;/span&gt; cho placeholder&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Tránh layout thrashing (batch read/write)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;" style="rounded=1;arcSize=10;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#FFFFFF;strokeColor=#b45309;strokeWidth=2;fontSize=11;fontColor=#78350f;align=left;verticalAlign=top;spacingLeft=12;spacingTop=8;fontFamily=Helvetica;shadow=0;" parent="1" vertex="1">
